  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1072">
<l>naṉṟaṟi vāriṟ kayavar tiruvuṭaiyār</l>
<l>neñcat tavala milar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The low enjoy more felicity than those who know what is good for the former are not troubled with anxiety (as to the good).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
